questions.question_text_1: Which of the following statement(s) is/are true regarding Single Page Applications (SPA) and Progressive Web Apps (PWA)?
question_texts: Which of the following statement(s) is/are true regarding Single Page Applications (SPA) and Progressive Web Apps (PWA)?

options.option_text: SPAs load entire web pages from the server for each user interaction.
PWAs can be installed on a user's device and accessed from the home screen.
SPAs often rely on client-side routing to update the content dynamically.
PWAs always require an internet connection to function.
SPAs may result in faster user experiences as they avoid full-page reloads.
PWAs use service workers to enable offline capabilities.
